# Resize Images

## Python Installation :

``` sh
sudo apt-get install python3
sudo apt-get install python3-pip
pip install --upgrade pip
```
## Resize Images installation :

``` sh
pip install resize-image
```

## Usage :

``` sh
fold-resize-images -d "path/to/directory" -W 150 -H 150
```
